These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, guinea-pig, chinchilla, rabbit
1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the rabbit##7
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Pet   | chinchilla | guinea-pig | rabbit | rat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, strawberry, blueberry, kale
1. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating kale##1
2. the person eating blueberry is somewhere between the person eating strawberry and the person eating potato##7
3. the person eating blueberry is between the person eating strawberry and the person eating kale##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | potato | kale | blueberry | strawberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
