.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, boat, car, roller
1. the person driving the roller is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the boat##7
2. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
3. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Transport   | car | subway | roller | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, romance, time-travel, action
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching action movies##2
3. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
4. the person watching epic movies is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching action movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | epic | romance | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, australian, japanese, british
1. the german is somewhere between the british and the australian##7
2. the japanese is somewhere between the german and the british##7
3. the japanese is on the left or right of the british##3
4. the japanese is somewhere to the right of the british##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| Nationality   | british | japanese | german | australian |

