.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, mirinda, water
1. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
2. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking soy-milk##7
3. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2     |   3   |      4      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | water | mirinda | soy-milk |

