3. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the taxi is somewhere between the person driving the bus and the person driving the tram##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | tram | car | taxi | bus |

